nguage><Type>General</Type><Text>The aparthotel Platja Daurada is situated in the centre of the Bay of Alcudia, next to the extensive beach of Ca'n Picafort. It is poplar with its visitors of different nationalities, many of whom return year after year to enjoy marvellous holidays.

In the hotel gardens you will find large swimming pools, a solarium with sunbeds and sunshades which will help you to relax. For those who prefer to practise some sport, our entertainment team have prepared a different programme for you each day, with fun and varied activities, both for children and adults. Sports tournaments and pool games are organised. There is also a Windsurf school. Massages can be booked at reception, which is available for you 24 hours a day for any query or information you may have or require.

At night, the entertainment team offers you a wide variety of shows, such as: Dance Night with an orchestra, acrobatics shows, entertainment team shows and of course, for the children, the Mini disco and games.

In the restaurant we serve an extensive breakfast buffet and at night a varied buffet evening meal, including "showcooking". At midday you can enjoy our homemade pizzas and snacks at the Pizzeria "UEP" next to the beach.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>SurroundingArea</Type><Text>The hotel is situated in Alcdia bay, well known for its calm, tranquil waters and long sandy beaches. Enjoy a lovely walk with superb views of the sea and the hills. There is a beautiful sandy beach near the hotel and sun loungers and parasols are available for hire at an additional cost. If you head to Alcudia, you will find the Roman village of Pollentia and, if you continue along the coast, you can see Pollena-one of the most beautiful villages in the region. There are also many interesting places to visit in the area surrounding the hotel. The Albufera nature reserve is just 2 km away and is worth a visit. Enjoy a pleasant stroll and admire the reserve's natural beauty. The reserve is of particular interest for bird watchers. The Aquapark is just 5 km from the hotel, with fun for all the family, including various water rides and features</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>RoomTypes</Type><Text>STANDARD - HOTEL - The rooms are equipped with:Air-conditioning (hot and cold), Satellite TV, Safe-deposit box (fee payable), Telephone, free WIFI, Full bathroom, Toiletry kit, Shower, Hairdryer, Possibility of cot, Fridge</Text></Description><Amenity><Code>Safe</Code><Text>Safe</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>AirConditioning</Code><Text>Air conditioning</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>RoomService</Code><Text>Room service</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HairDryer</Code><Text>Hair dryer</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Hairdresser</Code><Text>Hairdresser</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Bar</Code><Text>Bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>LaundryService</Code><Text>Laundry service</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>CarPark</Code><Text>Car parking</Text></